subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which emperor founded the city of Jaipur?
question_hi: जयपुर के स्थान कौन से प्राचीन महत्वकारी बनाई गई थी।
explanation_en: Dharmdas, also known as Sangram Singh, founded the city of Jaipur in 1727. He was a Rajput ruler and the founder of the Jaipur State.
